      "roles": ["Creative direction", "Art direction", "Creative toolkit", "Hands-on design", "Color", "Typography"],
      "bodyCopy": "Target and the creative team at Deutsch believe in kids so darn much, they hired a whole crew of them to create the campaign for back-to-school. Kid directors, kid stylists, kid illustrators and kid writers came together with grownup helpers to build a unique, kid-centric campaign from top-to-bottom. In her role as design director, Greta owned the campaign look-and-feel and built the toolkit, but the real highlight was coaching kid illustrators bringing the set designs to life.",
